name: IllinoisWirelessChecker
skdetail:

Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill connects to the wireless system at the University of Illinois and returns the total number of devices connected in each building. It also gives the number of wireless access points in each building to give context as to how busy each building actually is.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
